author: ZixuanJiang
message:
Add support for reduction factors and unreduced axes in the minimal version of explicit reshard.

If the following condition holds,
1. reduction factors are partitioned and have compatible sharding
2. results has unreduced axes

We insert the all-reduce along `axes_in_reduction_factors - unreduced_axes_in_the_result`. The JAX test `test_reduce_sum_unreduced` is an example.
